{"tid":410637,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"fb流傳何生喺新加坡疑似冇執業","createTime":"2017-09-23T06:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T08:16:45.000Z","uid":48083,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2828ffab801d6f12dfad4eafece0eb31c89b1ce","tid":410637,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:12:35.000Z","msg":"【何君堯疑沒有在新加坡執業】 #同英國情況一樣<br />\n何君堯除聲稱在英國執業外，也指在新加坡執業。我嘗試在新加坡的律師會 Directory搜尋&quot;Kwan Yiu Ho&quot; 及其他組合，全部是 No Result (見圖1)。<br />\n同時，我向律師會查詢沒有名字的情況，並剛得到回覆 (見圖2)。回覆指這情況是可能有註冊(admitted) 但現時並無執業 (currently not in practice)。而現時只有 Supreme Court of Singapore 有齊所有註冊律師的名字，並建議我向其查詢。<br />\n<br />\n換言之，何君堯需要解釋現時新加坡律師會的執業律師名冊並沒有他的名字，但卻在2016年選舉宣傳聲稱自己新加坡執業。估計最大可能性是他有註冊而沒有執業資格，或他用了一個一般人估不到的名字在新加坡登記。<br />\n<br />\n回信的全文：<br />\n<br />\nDear xxx,<br />\n <br />\nWe refer to your further email of 23 September 2017.<br />\n <br />\nThe directory you searched only maintain a list of lawyers who are currently in practice in Singapore and holding valid practising certificates. As explained earlier, Law Society maintains only a list of lawyers holding valid practising certificates. It is possible that Mr Junius Kwan Yiu Ho is admitted to the Singapore&rsquo;s Bar but as he is currently not in practice in Singapore, he is not listed in that directory or the Law Society&rsquo;s database.<br />\n <br />\nTo determine if a person is admitted to the Singapore&rsquo;s Bar, you may wish to check with the Supreme Court of Singapore as our Supreme Court maintains a &lsquo;roll of Advocates and Solicitors&rsquo; with the names of every person who was admitted to the Singapore&rsquo;s Bar, whether or not he is currently in practice. Do note that there is no directory available on the internet to check if a person is admitted to the Singapore&rsquo;s Bar.<br />\n <br />\nThank you.<br />\n <br />\nThe Law Society of Singapore<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/23/141051_755a22c3169b3762843182a93b0a5b13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F23%2F141051_755a22c3169b3762843182a93b0a5b13.jpg&h=690e277c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9350310d85039a23d1f5ca387cf36edcfa05c3fd","tid":410637,"uid":24339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:14:37.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"ee3300a9d445870c80aeb7e2ecdf714b3860d32c","tid":410637,"uid":13833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc81583689e66bcf4f2397152af0add3f5b212b1","tid":410637,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db70bd949fbf9441a444c2351dee55c34c564931","tid":410637,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n何生係香港律師資格點來？"},{"pid":"018d051ad882ddbcccd064d3cbc78bf72b63345f","tid":410637,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:25:18.000Z","msg":"愈來愈大單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07517a42572c43d6b020f78c5ec312039c4beba","tid":410637,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:26:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>愈來愈大單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965b578f94f4774ebacea1a45fbd5846f6fd5968","tid":410637,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T06:26:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n何生係香港律師資格點來？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似話讀完書，揾間支那行鳩簽俾佢就得"},{"pid":"799360798ef106005f8d20116c36bda29dab26d